channel.title: The road to my second 99 - Fletching
channel.description:
So I am going for the easiest cape in the game, Fletching.
I just achieved 99 cooking yesterday, and I want trimmed capes!
I can supposedly get 99 in less than a week, we shall see.
Started at level 70: Sunday, August 29
Got level 75: Sunday, August 29 Got level 82: Monday, August 30 Got level 86: Tuesday, August 31 Got level 90: Wednesday, September 1 Got level 92: Thursday, September 2 Got level 94: Friday, September 3
